document_data.name: Senityili
document_data.mainbody: '''Senityili''' was a [[sahuagin]] [[priestess]] of [[Sekolah]] in the [[City of Caverns]], among the [[Sea of Swords]].
document_data.Description: The cleric was dedicated to Sekolah, deity of [[shark]]s. She believed that a group of outsiders would aid the city, and thus treated them with far more respect than the rest of her kin.
document_data.Combat: She fought with a standard [[spear]] and knew an array of divine spells, the most powerful of which were ''[[blade barrier]]'' and ''[[slay living]]''.
document_data.History: Senityili lived in the City of Caverns. During the civil war in the city, she appeared to support King [[Ixilthetocal]]. Senityili believed in an old prophecy that told of the arrival of a stranger who would save the city.
